a think piece on...

01:11:31.636 --> 01:11:32.761
Hello?

01:11:32.929 --> 01:11:36.348
Hey, where were you? You were
supposed to be home an hour ago.

01:11:36.516 --> 01:11:39.727
- Uh... I bought the car.
