01:11:39.895 --> 01:11:43.022
I know it's a meaningless extravagance,
but I had to have it.

01:11:43.190 --> 01:11:45.191
- That thing we saw?
- Yeah.

01:11:45.358 --> 01:11:48.861
Did you hear Viking Press loved
the first four chapters of Ike's book?

01:11:49.029 --> 01:11:51.030
- Great!
- They were real complimentary.

01:11:51.198 --> 01:11:53.574
Next week I get the car
